'''韓國水電與核電公司'''（{{kor|諺=한국수력원자력|漢=韓國水力原子力(株)}}；{{lang-en|Korea Hydro & Nuclear Power}}，[[縮寫|縮寫]]： '''KHNP'''），是[[韓國電力公社|韓國電力公社]]（KEPCO）的[[子公司|子公司]]。其營運項目為在[[大韩民国|大韩民国]]的大型[[核电|核电]]與[[水力發電|水力發電]]廠，約佔該國40%的電力供應。KEPCO早在1977年時，於[[釜山|釜山]]的[[古里核电厂|古里核电厂]]開始[[核能發電|核能發電]]，1978年進行商轉；但KHNP公司是在2001年，因KEPCO重組被分離出來而正式成立<ref>{{cite web|url=http://cms.khnp.co.kr/eng/history/|title=History|work=KHNP English-language site|accessdate={{date|2014-11-19|mdy}}|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129123231/http://cms.khnp.co.kr/eng/history/|archivedate=2014-11-29}}</ref> 。

KHNP在[[紐約市|紐約市]]、[[亞特蘭大|亞特蘭大]]、[[巴黎|巴黎]]、[[東京|東京]]等地均設有辦公室，其現任的[[CEO|CEO]]為Cho Seok（조석）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://cms.khnp.co.kr/eng/history-of-excutives/ |title=History of Executives |work=KHNP English-language site |accessdate={{date|2014-11-19|mdy}} |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140301011626/http://cms.khnp.co.kr/eng/history-of-excutives/ |archivedate=2014-03-01 }}</ref> 。{{as of|2014}}，該公司大約有9,500員工<ref>{{cite web|url=http://cms.khnp.co.kr/eng/organizationpersonnel/|title=Organization & Personnel|work=KHNP English-language site|accessdate={{date|2014-11-19|mdy}}|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141020072856/http://cms.khnp.co.kr/eng/organizationpersonnel/|archivedate=2014-10-20}}</ref>，營收為7.3[[兆|兆]]韓圓 <ref>{{cite web |url=http://cms.khnp.co.kr/eng/financial-statements/ |title=Financial Statements |work=KHNP English-language site |accessdate={{date|2014-11-19|mdy}} |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141020050328/http://cms.khnp.co.kr/eng/financial-statements/ |archivedate=2014-10-20 }}</ref>（約60餘億[[美金|美金]]）。它當前的國際[[信用評級|信用評級]]是Aa3 穩定/A+ 穩定/AA- 穩定（[[穆迪|穆迪]]/[[標準普爾|標準普爾]]/[[惠譽|惠譽]]），<ref>{{cite web |url=http://cms.khnp.co.kr/eng/global-credit-ratings/ |title=Global Credit Ratings |work=KHNP English-language site |accessdate={{date|2014-11-19|mdy}} |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129123234/http://cms.khnp.co.kr/eng/global-credit-ratings/ |archivedate=2014-11-29 }}</ref> 在[[全世界|全世界]]的[[公共事業|公共事業]]評級中屬於前段。

2013年10月，該公司爆發了包含前CEO在內的100名員工集體偽造安全文件的醜聞。<ref name=wnn-20131010>{{cite news |url=http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/RS-Indictments_for_South_Korea_forgery_scandal-1010137.html |title=Indictments for South Korea forgery scandal |publisher=World Nuclear News |date=10 October 2013 |accessdate=14 October 2013 |archive-date=2015-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150220004328/http://www.world-nuclear-news.org/RS-Indictments_for_South_Korea_forgery_scandal-1010137.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=國外核能新聞|url=http://wapp4.taipower.com.tw/NSis/6/6_2query.php?firstid=6&secondid=2&thirdid=195|publisher=[[台灣電力公司|台灣電力公司]]|accessdate=2014-12-23|quote=這些安全有關控制纜線今年五月就已發現相關文件有偽造的嫌疑，而且相同的纜線還安裝於KHNP所屬的四個機組...|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141223210217/http://wapp4.taipower.com.tw/NSis/6/6_2query.php?firstid=6&secondid=2&thirdid=195|archivedate=2014-12-23}}</ref>

